The paper deals with robotics and machine learning techniques to enable robots to understand their high-level state and detect anomalies. Therefore, cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves the use of SVMs for classification, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves the use of data encoding and segmentation techniques, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper deals with the control and planning of robotic systems, which falls under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
